<div class="password-reset-container">
    <h2 class="page-title">Forgot Password?</h2>

    <div class="info-section">
        <h4>üí¢ Instructions (Not like I care if you mess up... but still!)</h4>
        <p>
          Ugh, fine! If you're having <em>trouble</em> logging into your precious editor or moderator account (of course you are...), 
          then <strong>maybe</strong>‚Äîjust <strong>maybe</strong>‚Äîthis form will help you reset your password.
          <br>Not that I'm doing it for you or anything!!
        </p>
      
        <h5>üîß Step 1: Bother the Webmaster (since you can't do anything yourself)</h5>
        <p>
          Go cry to a <strong>Webmaster</strong> and ask them‚Äî<em>politely</em>, okay?!‚Äîto reset your password.
          <br>Once they do, your current password will be <strong>obliterated</strong> and your login will be disabled.
          <br>So don't just sit there like an idiot!
        </p>
      
        <h5>üß† Step 2: Temporary Password... TRY NOT TO LOSE IT!!</h5>
        <p>
          The <strong>Webmaster</strong> (you better not annoy them) will give you a <strong>temporary password</strong>.
          <br>This password is <em>case-sensitive</em> and <strong>TOP SECRET</strong>, so don't go blabbing it to your friends or tattooing it on your forehead! Geez!
        </p>
      
        <h5>üìù Step 3: Use this Form (correctly, or else!)</h5>
        <p>
          In <em>this</em> form, you're supposed to enter:
          <ul>
            <li>Your <strong>username</strong> (YES, it's case-sensitive too‚Äîdon't mess it up!)</li>
            <li>The <strong>temporary password</strong> you just got</li>
            <li>Your shiny <strong>new password</strong>‚Äî<em>twice</em>, okay? TWICE. So you don't typo it like the clumsy fool you are!</li>
          </ul>
        </p>
      
        <p class="tsundere-note">
          ...And that's it. Don't expect me to walk you through it again! Hmph! It's not like I want to help you or anything‚Ä¶ <strong>b-baka! üò≥</strong>
        </p>
    </div>

    <% if (locals.errors && errors.length > 0) { %>
        <% errors.forEach(function(error) { %>
            <div class="alert alert-error">
                <%= error.msg %>
            </div>
        <% }); %>
    <% } %>

    <form id="passwordResetForm" class="password-reset-form" action="/admin/reset-password" method="POST">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="<%= csrfToken %>">
        
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="username">Username</label>
            <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required 
                   minlength="3" maxlength="20" placeholder="Enter your username">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="tempPassword">Temporary Password</label>
            <input type="password" id="tempPassword" name="tempPassword" required 
                   minlength="8" placeholder="Enter temporary password">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="newPassword">New Password</label>
            <input type="password" id="newPassword" name="newPassword" required 
                   minlength="8" placeholder="Enter new password">
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="confirmPassword">Confirm New Password</label>
            <input type="password" id="confirmPassword" name="confirmPassword" required 
                   minlength="8" placeholder="Confirm new password">
            <span id="passwordMatch" class="password-match-indicator"></span>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="submitButton">Reset Password</button>
    </form>
</div>